comments: This was fun! On several blocks the trial would start before I had a chance to click OK on the announcement popup, causing me to miss the very first image on several of the trials, so I just had to guess. Otherwise, there were no issues. Thank you.
strategy: For the majority of them, when I saw the images I mentally assigned a color description to each object and held the thought in my head of which color descriptor was assigned to the object. Occasionally I had to move the color wheel around until it 'felt' right. On the just a few instances I missed the first image completely (blink, drink a sip of coffee) and had to make a guess.
